>失真，<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">增大<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  D、NPN型BJT正常放大时，集电极是三个电极中电位最高的。共射极放大电路信号由集电极输出。当交流电压输出波形上半周失真时，意味着集电极电位已经不能再继续升高，集电极上电阻的压降几乎为零，也就是集电极电流已经过小，所以BJT处于截止状态，为截止失真。增加基极电流，使集电极电流增大，可以消除失真。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">用直流电压表测得放大电路中某<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">BJT<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">各管脚电位分别是<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">2V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">6V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">、<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">2.7V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，则三个电极分别是<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">___<span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">__<\/span>_<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">_<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，该管是<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">_<span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">__<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">_____<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">型。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">e<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">、<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">c<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">、<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">b<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">；<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">NPN<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、发射结压降的典型值为0.7伏（硅管）或0.2伏（锗管），且无论何种管型，基极电位总是处于中间值。而2.7V与2V差0.7V，所以是硅管，2.7V对应的电极是基极，那么2V对应的就是发射极，6V对应的就是集电极。又因为集电极电位最高，发射极电位最低，所以是NPN管（PNP管情况与此相反）。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:华康简宋;\">图示各电路中，能正常放大正弦交流信号的电路是<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">_____<span style=\"font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">__<\/span><\/span> <span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:华康简宋;\">（设各电容的容抗可忽略）。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">图<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">(b)<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、图中（a）电路中，对于交流通路而言，直流电压源置零，也就是接地，那么交流输入信号将会直接旁路到地，无法送入管子进行放大。  B、（c）电路中，电容Cb1隔断了基极的直流通路，因此发射结无法正偏，就无法工作在放大区。  C、（d）电路中，管子为NPN管，VBB可以满足发射结正偏，但是VCC接反，无法满足集电结反偏，因此管子无法工作在放大区。  D、（b）电路中，管子为NPN管，输入和输出都连接有耦合电容，在基极电阻和集电极电阻参数合理的情况下，可以使发射结正偏，集电结反偏，信号也可以正常输入输出，所以能正常放大交流信号。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">设原理图中<\/span>各电容容抗均可忽略，其小信号等效电路为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">________<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">图<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">(b)<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  A、将电路中电容置为短路，直流电压源置为接地，可知电路为共发射极电路，再将管子替换成小信号模型，可以得到小信号模型等效电路为图（b）。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:华康简宋;\">电路如图<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">(a)<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:华康简宋;\">所示，<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">若<em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Book Antiqua','serif';\">v<\/span><\/em><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">o<\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">中的交流成分出现图<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';\">(b)<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14p